						<div class="postbody">You need to save the buttons state from the <em>previous</em> frame. Then simply compare: &quot;if previous=0 AND current=1 =&gt; button has been pressed after previously being down&quot;.<br /><br />Some related links:<br /><!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=14809&amp;p=179274#p179274">viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=14809&amp;p=179274#p179274</a><!-- l --><br /><!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=12456&amp;p=142434#p142434">viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=12456&amp;p=142434#p142434</a><!-- l --></div>

					
